<br />

<br />
So my question is, 'Does the 39 charm song scale up to allowing 51's to be charmed or am I just doing something wrong?'
<br />

<br />
Thanks in advance  <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-10.gif" border="0" alt="Blushing" hspace="2" /></span></td>
