				<td colspan="2"><span>Two factors:
<br />

<br />
1)  If I am not mistaken, you can NEVER charm a mob higher level than you.
<br />

<br />
2)  Some mobs are flagged &quot;no-charmie,&quot; just like some mobs are flagged no-mezzie etc.  This becomes more and more common as you level up.  Named mobs in particular, are often flagged no-charmie.</span></td>
