				<td colspan="2"><span>You are mistaken, you can indeed charm mobs higher lvl then you. You just get much more resist.
<br />

<br />
I done my OT hammer this very exact way so the foreman WAS charmable back since 1 month ago. 
<br />

<br />
My guess is that the msg you are getting is &quot;that NPC cannot be charmed *with that spell*&quot;, you prolly need the song one step higher.
<br />

<br />
Beside, be aware that the hammer will not proc for you anyways untill you are 51 no hurries anyways  <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-5.gif" border="0" alt="Wink" hspace="2" /></span></td>
