				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: This NPC cannot be charmed?<a name="42314"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">May 26 04 10:03 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Note:  39 Charm song has an MR debuff component that IS effected by instrument modifiers.  If your charm lands, but doesn't stick, make sure you equip a Wind Instrument when the song lands.  That way, when the MR check happens every tick to see if it will break, their MR is lower.
<br />

<br />
Or go out and buy lots of CHA gear and come back and post a question about why your charms don't stick when your CHA is maxed.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
